2. **Code** (`lmsys_sample.py`, `maas_bench.py`) — MIT License

---

## Data: `lmsys_1000.jsonl`

`lmsys_1000.jsonl` is a filtered sample of [LMSYS-Chat-1M]
(https://huggingface.co/datasets/lmsys/lmsys-chat-1m), generated by
`lmsys_sample.py` in this repository. Only record-level selection was performed
(English conversations with 3–20 user turns); individual conversation contents
were not modified.

